title: Was the movie season "Smashing Your Feelings " 11 during the COVID-19 epidemic?
subtitle: The HBO series "Squish Your Emotion," which aired 10 seasons over 20 years, often left fans wondering when the show would return to a new season.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: The film "Squish Your Emotion" began filming the 11th season of it in November 2020, during the COVID-19 epidemic.
